    <p> To Mutti's luck, the Vivid Festival was still going throughout Sydney. So also in the Darling Harbor. Additional luck for her was that even today her favorite song was built into the water and light show. After that we went a small round along the harbor and marveled at the colorful -lit opera. </p>
    <p> But then I slowly had to be careful not to fall asleep while running. It was just a long journey. When we wanted to take the ferry back to the hotel, we unfortunately had to find that our ferry would not drive in the near future. So today we jumped into a taxi a third time and let ourselves go to the hotel via the Harbor Bridge. </p>
    <p> All in all, we really experienced a lot today, even if it didn't go according to plan. I think it was still a nice and successful day. </p>
    <p> Well then let's see what will happen in the next 4 weeks. <br> Good night </p>
